import React from 'react';
import { Grid, Card, CardContent, Typography, Box } from '@mui/material';
import PublicAlerts from '../../components/PublicAlerts';
import SafeHavenList from '../../components/SafeHavenList';
import CommunityResources from '../CommunityResources'; // Located in `features/CommunityResources`
import EmergencyContacts from '../EmergencyContacts'; // Located in `features/EmergencyContacts`
import SafetyTips from '../SafetyTips';


const CommunityDashboard: React.FC = () => {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ p: 3, backgroundColor: '#f5f5f5', minHeight: '100vh' }}>
      <Grid container spacing={3}>
        {/* Main Content Area */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={8}>
          <Grid container spacing={3}>
            <Grid item xs={12}>
              <Card>
                <CardContent>
                  <PublicAlerts />
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12}>
              <Card>
                <CardContent>
                  <SafeHavenList />
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>

        {/* Sidebar */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Grid container spacing={3}>
            <Grid item xs={12}>
              <Card>
                <CardContent>
                  <EmergencyContacts />
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12}>
              <Card>
                <CardContent>
                  <SafetyTips />
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12}>
              <Card>
                <CardContent>
                  <CommunityResources />
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default CommunityDashboard;
